main.java.com.djrapitops.plan.data

Class AnalysisData

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.com.djrapitops.plan.data.AnalysisData

  • public class AnalysisData
extends Object
    This class is used to store result data from Analysis at runtime. Most of the variables need to be set with various set methods, as they are not initialized in a constructor.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Rsl1122
    See Also:
    Analysis, PlaceholderUtils
